auto bridge
iface bridge
      bridge-vlan-aware yes
      bridge-ports glob node1-12 glob swp17-18 nas01-40 nas02-40 peerlink
      bridge-stp on
      bridge-vids 10 12
      mtu 9216

auto bridge.10
iface bridge.10
    address-virtual 10.9.10.1/24
    mtu 9216

auto bridge.12
iface bridge.12
    address-virtual 10.9.12.1/24
    mtu 9216

